### Teste de Deploy com site/aplicação parseado

POST http://localhost:5000/api/deploy
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_AQUI

{
  "repoUrl": "https://github.com/exemplo/teste-app.git",
  "branch": "main",
  "buildCommand": "npm run build",
  "buildOutput": "dist",
  "targetPath": "api",
  "iisSiteName": "gruppy/carteiras"
}

### Teste de Deploy no ROOT do site (sem applicationPath nem targetPath)

POST http://localhost:5000/api/deploy
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_AQUI

{
  "repoUrl": "https://github.com/LinkedFarma/Gruppy.Solution.Front",
  "branch": "dev",
  "buildCommand": "npm i && npm run build:main",
  "buildOutput": "core/main/dist",
  "iisSiteName": "gruppy"
}

### Teste de Deploy com aplicação separada (SEM targetPath - evita duplicação)

